events.name: ポイントクリック置き

parameters: ◆ プラグインコマンド 画像No、コモンイベントNo
1 クリックしたら、4 マウス置く、5 マウス離す

The river that continues far into the distance...
The embankment that continues far into the
distance...

Natsu: I wonder how we would cross this river if
there wasn't this bridge! There doesn't seem to be
any other way to cross this river.

Natsu: When I looked into the water, I found fish
swimming.

There are stairs over there. I wish we could go
fishing someday.
I have one more thing to look forward to.
I've been curious about that thing since earlier.

It's like a shop with a big sign that says
'Aoiya'! But when I looked closely, it had a flag
that said 'Dagashi'.

Misaki remembered that she had received pocket
money, so she put her hand into a small waist
pouch.
